data.description: This lovely well cared for home sits on a large oversized corner lot for plenty of privacy. The dining room is just off the entry and opens to the kitchen. The dining room features wood floors, chair rail, crown molding and tall ceilings. The kitchen is spacious and features tile floors, pantry, lovely wood cabinets and island. The breakfast nook has a bay window and vaulted ceilings. The family room is perfect for relaxing with wood floors, built in shelves, vaulted ceilings and wet bar with a sink. The cute sunroom is just off the formal living room. The large oversized formal living room is perfect for entertaining with a lovely fireplace. The primary bedroom is spacious with the primary bath featuring dual closets, dual sinks, garden tub and separate shower. The nice size guest bedrooms have large walk in closets. The guest bath has plenty of cabinet space and tile floors. The backyard has a lot of privacy with a wood fence and nice patio. Great location to shopping and schools!
